  <brief_title>Study of REGN475 in Patients With Pain Due to Osteoarthritis of the Knee or Hip</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Multi-Dose, Placebo-Controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of REGN475 in Patients With Pain Due to Osteoarthritis of the Knee or Hip</official_title>
  <sponsors>
