  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness of REGN475 compared to
      placebo in participants with pain due to osteoarthritis (OA) of the knee or hip and a history
      of inadequate joint pain relief or intolerance to current analgesic therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
